    "description": "Ensure that audit records contain information that establishes the following:<br />a. What type of event occurred;<br />b. When the event occurred;<br />c. Where the event occurred;<br />d. Source of the event;<br />e. Outcome of the event; and<br />f. Identity of any individuals, subjects, or objects/entities associated with the event.",
