    "description": "Upon termination of individual employment:<br />a. Disable system access within [Assignment: organization-defined time period];<br />b. Terminate or revoke any authenticators and credentials associated with the individual;<br />c. Conduct exit interviews that include a discussion of [Assignment: organization-defined information security topics];<br />d. Retrieve all security-related organizational system-related property; and<br />e. Retain access to organizational information and systems formerly controlled by terminated individual.",
